name: Touched by God, consumed by the hounds from Hell
description:
As people look towards their God for strength and security they are bound to Hell on Earth by self-illusion, doubt, lust, conceit, ignorance, and a craving for status & material goods.

Why wait for death to be saved? Why not take steps to better your life here on Earth and in turn better the world, one person at a time. Happiness and contentment lie within us all but to find it we must step away from those desires we crave so much.

The only thing we have control over in life is ourselves. We can control how we react to situations, people, and the environment. It is up to us to make a difference.

5400px X 7200 px by @dehiscenceart 2021.
